1. Definitions

   "Software" refers to the Vouch mod, its source code, compiled binaries,
   assets, documentation, and any associated files in this repository.

   "Author" refers to NozzDev and any authorized maintainers.

   "Official Distribution Channels" refers to the Author's pages on
   CurseForge, Modrinth, and GitHub Releases.

2. Permissions

   You MAY:

   a. View, study, and reference the source code for personal,
      educational, or development purposes.

   b. Fork and modify the source code for the purpose of submitting
      contributions (pull requests) back to the original repository.

   c. Include the unmodified Software in modpacks, provided the modpack
      does not charge for access to the Software itself and links back
      to an Official Distribution Channel for download.

   d. Use the Software on any number of Minecraft servers, including
      commercial servers, without restriction.

3. Restrictions

   You MAY NOT:

   a. Redistribute, re-upload, or mirror the Software (source or binary)
      on any platform, website, or file-sharing service outside of the
      Official Distribution Channels without prior written permission
      from the Author.

   b. Sell, sublicense, or commercially distribute the Software or any
      modified version of it.

   c. Create and distribute derivative works based on the Software.
      Forks for the purpose of contribution are permitted under 2(b).

   d. Remove, alter, or obscure this license, copyright notices, or
      author attribution from any copy of the Software.

4. Modpacks

   Inclusion in modpacks is permitted under the following conditions:

   a. The Software is not the primary selling point of the modpack.
   b. The Software is obtained from an Official Distribution Channel.
   c. Credit is given to the Author with a link to the project page.
   d. The modpack does not modify the Software's binaries.

